{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Carbinox Edge 7",
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Carbinox Edge 7",
      "category": "Custom"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}

<section class="carbinox-edge-7">
    <h2><span style="color: #FFC200;">EVERYTHING YOU NEED TO KNOW</span></h2>
    <div class="list-icons-7">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <img style="position: relative; bottom: -3px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0049/0533/6935/files/Group_97.png?v=1756826165" alt="icon" class="feature-icon" />
            <div>
                <p>BUILT FOR HARD WORK WITH A STAINLESS STEEL FRAME & GORILLA GLASS</p>
                <span>Engineered for durability, the Carbinox Edge is built with a reinforced stainless steel body and Gorilla Glass screen to resist drops, impact, scratches, and harsh job site conditions.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
                <div class="icon-container">
            <img style="position: relative; bottom: -3px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0049/0533/6935/files/Group_97.png?v=1756826165" alt="icon" class="feature-icon" />
            <div>
                <p>MAKE AND RECEIVE CALLS DIRECTLY FROM YOUR WRIST</p>
                <span>Stay connected without reaching for your phone. The Edge features built-in call functionality and mic/speaker system, so you can answer calls hands-free — even while wearing gloves.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
                <div class="icon-container">
            <img style="position: relative; bottom: -3px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0049/0533/6935/files/Group_97.png?v=1756826165" alt="icon" class="feature-icon" />
            <div>
                <p>LONG-LASTING 500MAH BATTERY – UP TO 14 DAYS PER CHARGE</p>
                <span>Forget daily charging. The Edge runs up to 14 days on a single charge with a pure cobalt 500mAh battery, making it perfect for extended shifts, travel, or weekend adventures.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
                <div class="icon-container">
            <img style="position: relative; bottom: -3px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0049/0533/6935/files/Group_97.png?v=1756826165" alt="icon" class="feature-icon" />
            <div>
                <p>DUAL-BAND GPS + 6 SATELLITE SYSTEMS FOR PRECISE TRACKING</p>
                <span>Whether you're hiking, working in remote areas, or navigating job sites, our upgraded GNSS tech ensures precise GPS tracking without relying solely on your smartphone.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
                <div class="icon-container">
            <img style="position: relative; bottom: -3px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0049/0533/6935/files/Group_97.png?v=1756826165" alt="icon" class="feature-icon" />
            <div>
                <p>170+ SPORTS MODES & 24/7 HEALTH MONITORING</p>
                <span>Track your performance across 170+ sports and activities. Monitor heart rate, blood oxygen, stress, sleep, and more — all with advanced onboard sensors.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
                <div class="icon-container">
            <img style="position: relative; bottom: -3px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0049/0533/6935/files/Group_97.png?v=1756826165" alt="icon" class="feature-icon" />
            <div>
                <p>IP69K & 5ATM WATERPROOF – READY FOR ANY ENVIRONMENT</p>
                <span>Designed to survive the elements, the Carbinox Edge is both IP69K dustproof and 5ATM waterproof — ready for mud, rain, snow, or submersion.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
                <div class="icon-container">
            <img style="position: relative; bottom: -3px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0049/0533/6935/files/Group_97.png?v=1756826165" alt="icon" class="feature-icon" />
            <div>
                <p>WORKS WITH THE CARBINOX MAX APP FOR FULL CONTROL</p>
                <span>Sync seamlessly with the Carbinox Max App (iOS & Android) to customize watch faces, access fitness data, adjust notifications, and get the most out of every feature</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .carbinox-edge-7 {
        background: black;
        padding: 60px 20px;
    }
    .icon-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-start;
    }
    .icon-container img {
        margin-top: -4px;
    }
    .carbinox-edge-7 h4, .carbinox-edge-7 h2{
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: white;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        line-height: 120%;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .list-icons-7 {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
        max-width: 1140px;
        margin: auto;
    }
    .list-icons-7 p {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: white;
        line-height: 120%;
    }

    .list-icons-7 span {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: white;
        line-height: 100%;
    }
</style>